<div class="field-items">
<div class="field-item even">4. How long do we store personal data?</div>
</div>
</div>
<div aria-expanded="false" aria-hidden="true" aria-labelledby="ui-accordion-ui-id-1-header-3" class="group-accordion-body field-group-div ui-accordion-content ui-helper-reset ui-widget-content ui-corner-bottom" id="field-collection-item-field-accordion-full-group-accordion-body--4" role="tabpanel" style="display: none;">
<div class="acc-wrapper">
<div class="field field-name-field-inner-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
<div class="field-items">
<div class="field-item even">
<p>We will only retain your personal data for as long as necessary to fulfil the purpose for which it was collected or to comply with legal or regulatory requirements.</p>
</div>
